definition.value: The interopercle ossifies in the interoperculomandibular ligament, which attaches to the retroarticular. The interopercle approximates and is ligamentously attached to the retroarticular anteroventrally. ZDB-PUB-961014-192.  Need develops_in relationship for interopercle.
